{"name": "kaldi-native-fbank", "metadata": {"name": "kaldi-native-fbank", "version": "1.20.1", "classifiers": ["Programming Language :: C++", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Topic :: Scientific/Engineering :: Artificial Intelligence"], "home_page": "https://github.com/csukuangfj/kaldi-native-fbank", "license": "Apache licensed, as found in the LICENSE file", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": null, "upload_time": 1729772145}, "documentation": ["# Introduction\n\nKaldi-compatible online fbank feature extractor without external dependencies.\n\nTested on the following architectures and operating systems:\n\n  - Linux\n  - macOS\n  - Windows\n  - Android\n  - x86\n  - arm\n  - aarch64\n\n# Usage\n\nSee the following CMake-based speech recognition (i.e., text-to-speech) projects\nfor its usage:\n\n- <https://github.com/k2-fsa/sherpa-ncnn>\n  - Specifically, please have a look at <https://github.com/k2-fsa/sherpa-ncnn/blob/master/sherpa-ncnn/csrc/features.h>\n- <https://github.com/k2-fsa/sherpa-onnx>\n\nThey use `kaldi-native-fbank` to compute fbank features for **real-time**\nspeech recognition.\n\n# Python APIs\n\nFirst, please install `kaldi-native-fbank` by\n\n```bash\ngit clone https://github.com/csukuangfj/kaldi-native-fbank\ncd kaldi-native-fbank\npython3 setup.py install\n```\n\nor use\n\n```bash\npip install kaldi-native-fbank\n```\n\nTo check that you have installed `kaldi-native-fbank` successfully, please use\n\n```\npython3 -c \"import kaldi_native_fbank; print(kaldi_native_fbank.__version__)\"\n```\n\nwhich should print the version you have installed.\n\nPlease refer to\n\n  - <https://github.com/csukuangfj/kaldi-native-fbank/blob/master/kaldi-native-fbank/python/tests/test_online_fbank.py>\n  - <https://github.com/csukuangfj/kaldi-native-fbank/blob/master/kaldi-native-fbank/python/tests/test_online_mfcc.py>\n\nfor usages.\n\nFor easier reference, we post the above file below:\n\n```python3\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\nimport sys\n\ntry:\n    import kaldifeat\nexcept:\n    print(\"Please install kaldifeat first\")\n    sys.exit(0)\n\nimport kaldi_native_fbank as knf\nimport torch\n\n\ndef main():\n    sampling_rate = 16000\n    samples = torch.randn(16000 * 10)\n\n    opts = kaldifeat.FbankOptions()\n    opts.frame_opts.dither = 0\n    opts.mel_opts.num_bins = 80\n    opts.frame_opts.snip_edges = False\n    opts.mel_opts.debug_mel = False\n\n    online_fbank = kaldifeat.OnlineFbank(opts)\n\n    online_fbank.accept_waveform(sampling_rate, samples)\n\n    opts = knf.FbankOptions()\n    opts.frame_opts.dither = 0\n    opts.mel_opts.num_bins = 80\n    opts.frame_opts.snip_edges = False\n    opts.mel_opts.debug_mel = False\n\n    fbank = knf.OnlineFbank(opts)\n    fbank.accept_waveform(sampling_rate, samples.tolist())\n\n    assert online_fbank.num_frames_ready == fbank.num_frames_ready\n    for i in range(fbank.num_frames_ready):\n        f1 = online_fbank.get_frame(i)\n        f2 = torch.from_numpy(fbank.get_frame(i))\n        assert torch.allclose(f1, f2, atol=1e-3), (i, (f1 - f2).abs().max())\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    torch.manual_seed(20220825)\n    main()\n    print(\"success\")\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "kaldi-native-fbank.python.tests.test_rfft", "documentation": ["!/usr/bin/env python3", "Copyright (c)  2021-2023  Xiaomi Corporation (authors: Fangjun Kuang)"], "functions": [{"name": "kaldi-native-fbank.python.tests.test_rfft.test_rfft", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "kaldi-native-fbank.python.tests.test_rfft.main", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "kaldi-native-fbank.python.tests.test_mel_bank_options", "documentation": ["!/usr/bin/env python3", "Copyright (c)  2021  Xiaomi Corporation (authors: Fangjun Kuang)"], "functions": [{"name": "kaldi-native-fbank.python.tests.test_mel_bank_options.test_default", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "kaldi-native-fbank.python.tests.test_mel_bank_options.test_set_get", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "kaldi-native-fbank.python.tests.test_mel_bank_options.test_from_empty_dict", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "kaldi-native-fbank.python.tests.test_mel_bank_options.test_from_dict_partial", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "kaldi-native-fbank.python.tests.test_mel_bank_options.test_from_dict_full_and_as_dict", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "kaldi-native-fbank.python.tests.test_mel_bank_options.test_pickle", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "kaldi-native-fbank.python.tests.test_mel_bank_options.main", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "kaldi-native-fbank.python.tests.test_frame_extraction_options", "documentation": ["!/usr/bin/env python3", "Copyright (c)  2022  Xiaomi Corporation (authors: Fangjun Kuang)"], "functions": [{"name": "kaldi-native-fbank.python.tests.test_frame_extraction_options.test_default", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "kaldi-native-fbank.python.tests.test_frame_extraction_options.test_set_get", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "kaldi-native-fbank.python.tests.test_frame_extraction_options.test_from_empty_dict", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "kaldi-native-fbank.python.tests.test_frame_extraction_options.test_from_dict_partial", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "kaldi-native-